description:
&lt;p&gt;Herts Valleys CCG is looking for dynamic experienced individual with good communication skills who are interested in developing their leadership and management skills as well as extending their current portfolio of skills and ability to fill the role of CHC assessor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are seeking applications from individuals who are a registered nurse or Occupational Therapist with the experience of undertaking care needs assessments, case and risk and management in supporting patients and their families through the Continuing Healthcare process.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;To achieve this you will require working knowledge and experience of the National Framework of Continuing Healthcare and associated tools.&lt;br /&gt;You will be supported in achieving further professional qualifications and development in these key and exciting roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous applicants need not apply&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sylvia Walker-Spiers/ Chris Brown&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clinical Lead&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;chris.brown24@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
